{"tid":505268,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓國產手機最貴4-5萬港元   夠買一噸糧食","createTime":"2017-12-21T02:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T15:09:06.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d27bb6cc0a9ad1fddd96da8a8046c5905714daf","tid":505268,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"當大家還在考慮要不要買蘋果最新的iPhone X手機之際，其實不妨也考慮一下由北韓自主研發的智能手機，因為擁有一部，這才能算是「有地位、有錢財」的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n北韓自2010年開始研發適合各年齡階層的手機，使智能手機開始擴散至生活之中，成為了「富貴階層」的象徵，當地一部手機售價由約5000港元至約4.5萬港元不等，這個價錢在平壤至少能買到115公斤至1噸糧食，或是2400公斤粟米。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/103427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F103427_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d3ace321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">北韓人普遍使用「阿里郎」或是「平壤」牌手機</span><br />\n<br />\n北韓國產手機在推出初期，都還是折疊或按鍵式，一直到2014年才正式推出觸控螢幕手機。第一款智能手機為「阿里郎AS1201」，之後又陸續推出了金達萊、阿里郎151和161，以及171、平壤2417和2419、金阿里郎、小觸控、雙面觸控、阿里郎FP68等智能手機，其中最受歡迎的便是金阿里郎、小觸控和雙面觸控。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/103644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F103644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ceb5af93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金阿里郎是鍍金手機，小觸控手機是針對喜歡新鮮事物的年輕人製作而成，外觀小巧又可愛，據說特別受到年輕女性的青睞。北韓消息人士稱，小觸控手機價格低廉，卻具備了智能手機的基本功能，所以廣受當地人民喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/103705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F103705_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=88c4d0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">北韓第一款國產智慧型手機「阿里郎AS1201」</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然說北韓自2010年已開始有國產手機，但不知是否對自家產品沒有信心，領袖金正恩曾於2013年1月26日被外界發現使用台灣宏達電（hTC）手機。直至他於2013年8月視察平壤手機工廠時，才不斷稱讚國產手機「阿里郎」好看又輕便，照相的畫素又超高，瘋狂試玩「阿里郎」手機，但不知金正恩現在是使用甚麼手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/103758_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F103758_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=135b0f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">金正恩曾視察手機生產。</span><br />\n<br />\n北韓所有手機都需要另外購買電話卡。有消息人士稱，連手機原本附帶的物件都要單賣，更不可能免費提供SIM卡，而SIM卡價格是依據容量而定，最便宜的約為11港元，貴的約8.5港元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2684837-北韓國產手機最貴4-5萬港元-夠買一噸糧食/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2684837-%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%94%A2%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B44-5%E8%90%AC%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83-%E5%A4%A0%E8%B2%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%99%B8%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%2F&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=ffac93cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2684837-北韓國產手機最貴4-5萬港元-夠買一噸糧食/</a>"},{"pid":"3046b8fe35378e283a5a2b809121ac3df76b0d0a","tid":505268,"uid":133883,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"最便宜的約為11港元，貴的約8.5港元。？？？<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"fe773701456f030c2f476a5d0d1dbfb3c310c325","tid":505268,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最便宜的約為11港元，貴的約8.5港元。？？？<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60db4a2489b6133a039f62fbdac77224e8f20041","tid":505268,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最便宜的約為11港元，貴的約8.5港元。？？？<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n超市價格、、 普通價8.5 做特價就11蚊"},{"pid":"fa16c9137e9ddb6933b4bf3ecfa8d7d336d6068c","tid":505268,"uid":28277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"連食物都冇，會有人買電話？"},{"pid":"74d797a9c45af040ecaa2f115334ef92260dbc87","tid":505268,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebf40ad922c47d8c45dd4813d68061055f30138","tid":505268,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最便宜的約為11港元，貴的約8.5港元。？？？<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec8d720d43913524557bb19203f90d5abc37e9a","tid":505268,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T14:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9979d176e56cc194c50a36d6c36122e78ff82e5c","tid":505268,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"真係慘"}]}